<main id="content" class="content"> <header> <h1 class="title">Prayer for Advent 4</h1>
 <p class="subtitle" role="doc-subtitle">Dec 20, 2016 00:00</p>
</header> <p>
Father of Light,
</p>

 <p>
The creator of the universe <br></br>
came to us as a helpless child, <br></br>
reminding us that there is no <br></br>
reconciliation without risk <br></br>
or love without a chance of loss.
</p>

 <p>
But we sacrificed peace <br></br>
on the altar of security, <br></br>
preferring to remain in darkness <br></br>
than to venture out into the light, <br></br>
desiring our kingdom more than yours.
</p>

 <p>
Give us the courage <br></br>
to drop our guard, <br></br>
and open our lives <br></br>
both to you and <br></br>
to one another.
</p>

 <p>
 <i>Amen</i>
</p>


